title: Ashes Of Ares - Ashes Of Ares 320k  MP3  ak2014
description:
Ashes Of Ares - Ashes Of Ares 320k  MP3  ak2014 What we got ..Ashes Of Ares is an American heavy metal group featuring ex-Iced Earth frontman Matt Barlow on vocals, Freddy Vidales on guitars, and Van Williams (formerly of the band Nevermore) on drums.

Contents

    1 History

    

On June 2012, Barlow announced on his Facebook page the creation of a new band with former Iced Earth bassist Freddie Vidales and Nevermore drummer Van Williams. Later that year the band signed with Nuclear Blast Records and entered Morrisound studio and recorded their debut self-titled album. The album was released on September 6th 2013. 
The band went on tour around Europe with Powerwolf and Battlebeast in September/October 2013.
